{"tid":1542764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[港交所出事] 許繹彬: 於證券行業從事廿多年，均沒有出現今日類似情況","createTime":"2019-09-05T03:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T03:14:47.000Z","uid":161430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"549ad23df2ac172da154fc154ef4ea237277f703","tid":1542764,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:14:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190905/60011269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F60011269&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6rubXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=e5a3582c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F60011269&h=ab2be949\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190905/60011269</a><br />\n<br />\n昨日港股喪炒撤回《逃犯條例》修訂消息而升近千點，有投資者趁消息炒一轉。不過今早有操作期指的投資者表示，未能進行期指買賣。<br />\n<br />\n有認購證發行商表示，期指市場今早出現問題，很多人交易不到，電腦不能落盤，成交全以人手操作。有交易商表示，今早9時30分過後，成交買賣速度很慢，相當不正常，交易量亦較平時少，差價亦很闊，指期交所連線有問題，<span style=\"color: orange;\">平台亦連接不到</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有散戶投資者向記者表示，今早欲加注買期權，但平台像沒反應，<span style=\"color: orange;\">難以交易</span>。<br />\n<br />\n耀才證券行政總裁許繹彬表示，<span style=\"color: orange;\">於證券行業從事廿多年，均沒有出現今日類似情況</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">「冇諗過會咁」</span>，他指在9時30分左右出現斷線問題。但不會揣測交易所發生甚麼事，現時期貨客戶中至少九成無法交易，「唔止平唔到倉，好多人直情交易唔到，公司都收多咗電話，係<span style=\"color: orange;\">全行都有問題</span>。」但他估計，並非如消息般指SPTrader出事，因為<span style=\"color: orange;\">是交易所出事</span>。<br />\n<br />\n宏匯資產管理董事及投資總監林嘉麒表示，今早期指市場未能落盤，由於其客戶主要操作現貨為主，因此較少客戶受影響。<br />\n<br />\n不過，<span style=\"color: orange;\">直至10時48分，港交所網頁亦死機</span>，出了「無法連上這個網站」字樣。<br />\n<br />\n港交所發言人表示，已得悉旗下衍生產品市場系統出現連接問題，正了解情況，並會在適時提供最新資訊。<br />\n<br />\n截至10時37分，恒指期貨交易張數17,635張，較正常水平為少，昨日全日成交為27萬張。<br />\n有連登網民將事件與林鄭稍後11時15分見記者聯繫一起聯想，網民「一個」笑稱，「想出緊急法但又怕股市大跌，可以點？禁止買賣咪得囉。」「日夜思湘」亦擔心「林鄭11點開記者會，有無可能係緊急法？」"},{"pid":"8cc7169dff73342157a92773b08cae300c3c6976","tid":1542764,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:14:47.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}